<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, February 23 (Xinhua) -- A four-year-old girl Sunday died
of meningitis in Boiscommun, a town of the Loire region in central
France, triggering fear of a contamination of the epidemic rare in
France, reported Agence France-Presse Monday.
</P>
