<P>
A group of between 15 to 20 gunmen broke into the Headquarters
of the United Nations Observer Mission in Georgia last Thursday
and took the four military observers hostage. Two rounds of talks
have been held between the government of Georgia and the gunmen on
the release of the hostages.
