Countries to participate in the UNDP training are Brazil,
China, Ethiopia, India, Iran, Japan, Mexico, Mongolia, Peru,
Russia, Slovakia, Trinidad and Tobago, Turkey, Ukraine and the
United States, UNDP said in a press release today. 
