Three countries including Germany, England and South Africa
have confirmed they will bid for the 2006 World Cup.
</P>
<P>
Germany has claimed early that it had a deal with England to
let it be the sole European candidate.
</P>
<P>
But Pele said he did not think the current fierce feud had been
settled between England and Germany for the nomination by the
European football powers. 
