care for their children. We feel the same should apply when it
comes to Iraq, they are also god's children.
</P>
<P>
"The use of force is not synonymous with democratic principles
for which America is a great believer and preacher," he said.
</P>
<P>
Nyirenda said that Africa and the Arab world need development
and not wars and that the choice of leadership in Iraq is the
prerogative of the Iraqi people just as it is the choice of
americans to choose a leader of their choice. 
