<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, February 24 (Xinhua) -- The fast-growing economy
together with low inflation in east China's Jiangsu Province made
the local per capita GDP in 1997 exceed 1,000 US dollars by
reaching 9,364 yuan.
</P>
<P>
Jiangsu's GDP last year was 669.5 billion yuan, as a result of
local efforts to promote all-round economic development.
</P>
