wrestling team to Tehran, which was warmly welcomed by Iranians.
</P>
<P>
The wrestlers arrived here last Tuesday to attend the Takhti
Cup international wrestling tournament. It has been the first
U.S. delegation to visit Iran since the two countries broke
diplomatic relations in 1980 after the Islamic Revolution in
1979. 
