Belarus 7-6 (7-1), 6-2 while Julie Halard-Decugis of France
blitzed Kristie Boogert of The Netherlands 6-3, 6-2.
</P>
<P>
Top-seeded Lindsay Davenport plays her first match on
Wednesday, while the Williams sisters, third-seeded Venus Williams
and fifth-seeded Serena Williams, begin tournament play
Tuesday. 
