<HEADLINE> Xiamen Opens Patented Technology Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XIAMEN, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Xiamen, a special economic
zone in east China's Fujian Province, has opened China's first
patented technology zone.
</P>
